<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>TWZ</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 03:30:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>地堡谈话：美利坚合众国版 250 岁生日快乐！</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-happy-250th-birthday-united-states-of-america-edition</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国两个半世纪。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-happy-250th-birthday-united-states-of-america-edition"&gt;后邦克谈话：美利坚合众国版 250 岁生日快乐！&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 20:44:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-happy-250th-birthday-united-states-of-america-edition</guid></item><item><title>克里米亚俄罗斯空军基地的加固飞机掩体因乌克兰无人机袭击而受损（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/hardened-aircraft-shelters-at-russian-air-base-in-crimea-damaged-from-ukrainian-drone-strikes</link><description>&lt;p&gt;对萨基空军基地的无人机袭击是乌克兰最新行动的一部分，目的是让克里米亚尽可能不适合俄罗斯军队居住。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/hardened-aircraft-shelters-at-russian-air-base-in-crimea-damaged-from-ukrainian-drone-strikes"&gt;克里米亚俄罗斯空军基地的加固飞机掩体因乌克兰无人机袭击而受损（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 20:16:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/hardened-aircraft-shelters-at-russian-air-base-in-crimea-damaged-from-ukrainian-drone-strikes</guid></item><item><title>这就是即将飞越首都上空的庞大空中舰队</title><link>https://www.twz.com/space/this-is-the-massive-aerial-armada-that-is-about-to-fly-over-the-capital</link><description>&lt;p&gt;NASA 将带领一波又一波的飞机（从隐形轰炸机到 VIP 直升机）飞越购物中心，庆祝美国 250 岁生日。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这篇文章&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/space/this-is-the-massive-aerial-armada-that-is-about-to-fly-over-the-capital"&gt;“这是即将飞越首都的大型空中舰队”&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 18:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/space/this-is-the-massive-aerial-armada-that-is-about-to-fly-over-the-capital</guid></item><item><title>英国皇家海军海上发射经过实战验证的 Nyan Kamikaze 无人机，预示着舰队的“混合”未来</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/royal-navys-sea-launch-of-combat-proven-nyan-kamikaze-drone-points-to-fleets-hybrid-future</link><description>&lt;p&gt;新的舰载打击能力的展示是在推进无人机在整个舰队中深度整合的计划之际进行的。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/royal-navys-sea-launch-of-combat-proven-nyan-kamikaze-drone-points-to-fleets-hybrid-future"&gt;英国皇家海军海上发射经过战斗验证的 Nyan Kamikaze 无人机预示着舰队的“混合”未来&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 17:20:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/royal-navys-sea-launch-of-combat-proven-nyan-kamikaze-drone-points-to-fleets-hybrid-future</guid></item><item><title>美国海军 MH-60S 海鹰在阿拉伯海坠毁（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/mh-60s-seahawk-goes-down-in-arabian-sea-search-on-for-missing-crewmember</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在其他三人被安全找到后，搜寻失踪船员的工作正在进行。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/mh-60s-seahawk-goes-down-in-arabian-sea-search-on-for-missing-crewmember"&gt;美国海军 MH-60S 海鹰在阿拉伯海坠落（更新）&lt;/a&gt;后首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 10:58:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/mh-60s-seahawk-goes-down-in-arabian-sea-search-on-for-missing-crewmember</guid></item><item><title>海军新型“末日飞机”被推迟，监管机构称发展问题现已成为现实</title><link>https://www.twz.com/nuclear/navys-new-doomsday-plane-delayed-as-watchdog-says-developmental-concerns-are-now-realities</link><description>&lt;p&gt;GAO 此前曾质疑海军选择基于 C-130 的飞机来满足其核指挥和控制需求。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;监督机构称发展问题&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;现已&lt;/a&gt;成为&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/nuclear/navys-new-doomsday-plane-delayed-as-watchdog-says-developmental-concerns-are-now-realities"&gt;现实，海军新型“末日飞机”被推迟&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jul 2026 22:36:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/nuclear/navys-new-doomsday-plane-delayed-as-watchdog-says-developmental-concerns-are-now-realities</guid></item><item><title>报告得出结论，俄罗斯“极有可能”是无人机入侵英国美国基地的幕后黑手</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/russia-highly-likely-behind-drone-incursions-over-u-s-bases-in-england-report-concludes</link><description>&lt;p&gt;IISS 研究组织的调查结果是对俄罗斯在 2024 年以来席卷欧洲的无人机入侵中所扮演角色的更广泛调查的一部分。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/russia-highly-likely-behind-drone-incursions-over-u-s-bases-in-england-report-concludes"&gt;无人机入侵英国美军基地报告结论称，俄罗斯“极有可能”是幕后&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;黑手&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jul 2026 22:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/russia-highly-likely-behind-drone-incursions-over-u-s-bases-in-england-report-concludes</guid></item><item><title>海军已经在寻找其全新 AARGM-ER 雷达破坏导弹的替代品（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/navy-already-looking-for-alternatives-to-its-brand-new-aargm-er-radar-busting-missile</link><description>&lt;p&gt;经过多年的拖延，海军正在推动 AGM-88G AARGM-ER 的最终部署，但现在也在考虑其他选择。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/navy-already-looking-for-alternatives-to-its-brand-new-aargm-er-radar-busting-missile"&gt;海军已经在寻找其全新 AARGM-ER 雷达破坏导弹的替代品（更新）的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jul 2026 17:23:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/navy-already-looking-for-alternatives-to-its-brand-new-aargm-er-radar-busting-missile</guid></item><item><title>F-15EX 和幽灵蝙蝠在英勇之盾期间在太平洋上空联手</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/f-15ex-and-ghost-bat-team-up-over-pacific-during-valiant-shield</link><description>&lt;p&gt;它们在 Valiant Shield 期间的共同亮相发出了迄今为止最强烈​​的信号：Eagle II 将演变成协作战斗无人机的控制器。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/f-15ex-and-ghost-bat-team-up-over-pacific-during-valiant-shield"&gt;F-15EX 和幽灵蝙蝠在英勇之盾期间在太平洋上空组队&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jul 2026 17:20:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/f-15ex-and-ghost-bat-team-up-over-pacific-during-valiant-shield</guid></item><item><title>B-52 同温层堡垒轰炸机在伊朗战争部署后离开英国</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/b-52-stratofortress-bombers-leave-england-after-iran-war-deployment</link><description>&lt;p&gt;B-52 离开以及其他资产最近回国，正值美国和伊朗之间的紧张谈判之际。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/b-52-stratofortress-bombers-leave-england-after-iran-war-deployment"&gt;伊朗战争部署后 B-52 同温层堡垒轰炸机离开英国的&lt;/a&gt;照片首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jul 2026 00:05:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/b-52-stratofortress-bombers-leave-england-after-iran-war-deployment</guid></item></channel></rss>